name: Douge
description: Douge is the first meme coin built on the Telos EVM. Upon launch on the 10th November 2021, 50% of the supply was allocated into Douglas Horn's wallet, an independant guardian and one of the principle architects behind the Telos blockchain. Douge is a light hearted and fun project, built by the community, for the community to celebrates the Telos EVM and proivde a platform for sharing memes and ideas.
